name: PLINQ Buitendienst Mobile App

### Welcome to Plinq Mobile APP
This is the APP we're creating for the Dutch company PLINQ BV

If you're using the GitHub for Mac, simply sync your repository and you'll see the new branch.

### Ionic Templates
We've created this app with help of Ionic Angular. For reference we link to http://ionicframework.com/

### Authors and Contributors
Danny Hoeve @cacanny  & Mike Mijnheer @MikeMijnheer
